Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:09.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kagami Yoshimizu Theater"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit screwing around and start!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ambiguous 3cm?\NDoes that mean it's plushy? Wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wrapping is a uniform, argh,\Nit's not an act, pooh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta do your best, gotta just do it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's time to catch 'n' release, eek{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Between sweat (whoop)\NSweat (whoop){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Darlin', darlin', freeze! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kinda lethargic,\Nsomething's kinda comin' out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you... Oh wait,\None of those was different{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worrywarts, high metal bars {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tasty thoughts... And that's enough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The heated body of that\Nflying you-know-who{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's what you call a normal girlie{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I the only one surprised? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seconds on pork-bone broth ramen\Nwith wire-hard noodles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Da da da da da {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pom-poms cheer squad{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's get cherry pie {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Happy fun welcoming party {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.87,0:00:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look up! Sensation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.46,0:00:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah! Feeling of existence,\Ndot dot small planet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:00:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Collided and it melted away,\Nin total awe{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go all out to sing, shi-ranger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take it away! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should be the one who'll be\Nlaughing in the end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.49,0:01:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I have the sailor suit\N← This is my conclusion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's only Monday! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Already in a bad mood? What to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really prefer the summer outfits\N← kya! Wah! Good! (cute!) < 3{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until we approach 3 pixels,\Nno hesitations please ★{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.39,0:01:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do your best, be energetic {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My darlin', darlin' please! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, we're wearing\Nthe summer uniforms starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Konata will still come\Nin the winter uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.07,0:01:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's always at least one person\Nin every class that forgets.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.55,0:01:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, there was someone\Nso close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Various People"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:02:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I forgot to apply for\Nthe giveaway in {\i1}The Tele{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.92,0:02:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn, I was kinda going after\Nthat apron from {\i1}Love Apron{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just didn't have enough love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have enough love,\NKagami, so you forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.16,0:02:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was really busy lately
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the committee stuff\Nand studying for exams...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, those are only excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never forgotten, not even once!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't compare me to you!\NYou only think of playing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, how you phrased it\Njust now is really irritating.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you win those\Ngiveaways, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In one word: Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'm a woman with no love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you send in a normal postcard,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll lose where you otherwise\Nstood a chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you write your\Npostcards, Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I make them to win, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neat handwriting is the\Nmost basic of fundamentals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to write a postcard\Nthat the choosers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would just want to\Nget into their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, use a highlighter to\Ndraw a border on the postcard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that really shows up well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, you add an illustration,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a motif of the item\Nthat you want to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An illustration?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can draw very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People of that sort resort to numbers,\Nand send in many cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, even when\Nyou're submitting a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't use a printer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to make sure to write\Neach and every one by hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And send a hundred at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred is like normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That costs a fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so that you can\Nget what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need both enthusiasm\Nand investment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't there a time when\Nit's cheaper to just buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things in this world\Nthat money can't buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred postcards...\NDo they fit in a mailbox?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't put them in all at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you send them in small portions,\Na few at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you have to spread it\Nover several days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you have a lot of cards at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the chooser might\Nshove all of them aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:04:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there are times when it's best\Nto not be so desperate,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and times when the opposite is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's all about love!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, if you want\Nto win something,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,check out free handouts or flyers\Nfolded into newspapers as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and apply for something that\Ndoesn't look too popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chances of winning\Nare pretty high then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll try that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the love in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, Tsukasa... You sure\Ndon't look alike, for being twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we're fraternal twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the difference is more\Nlike ordinary sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Identical twins come from one egg\Nand really do look alike,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but fraternal twins can be different\Nin appearance and personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that Tsukasa is so laid-back,\Nbut Kagami is vicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, how scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe if we set your hairdo\Nand ribbons in the same way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you might look more alike\Nthan we think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good, it's impossible to put\Nsomething cute on you, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Don't go imagining\Nsomething on your own
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and saying something rude from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have something\Nlike telepathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, how twins can be far apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but somehow they have\Nthe same lifestyle habits
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or same taste in the opposite gender,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even marry other twins and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, and like when one is in danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the other can sense it from\Nsomewhere completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are all sorts of strange\Nphenomenon out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you have telepathy\Nor something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you try it out right now.\NLike, beep-beep-beep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just you reading\Ntoo much manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana-Kana, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana-Kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them were saying how\Nthey were slightly different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how Mana's the one\Nwho's really cautious,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Kana's the one who's optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they said their voices were\Nslightly different when they sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana-Kana had always thought\Nthat they were fraternal twins,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they recently found out that\Nthey actually were identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is that something to be\Nso surprised about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The definition of identical and\Nfraternal twins changed recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means there's\Nthe possibility that you two
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are identical twins as well,\NKagami, Tsukasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The similarities between you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you like sweets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I love them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you are left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your favorite color?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same colors as your souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, with all this talk of eggs\Nand sausage, I'm getting hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't talking about food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so muggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We end up sweating as soon\Nas it gets a little crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting to be\Nthat time of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't turned on\Nthe air conditioning yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ladybug samba, punk version...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:56.81,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"We Kiyotaka Narumi and Yui Kobayakawa,\Nare getting married \Nthis coming XXth of June."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of my relatives is\Ngetting married this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, a June bride! That's so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is such a wet,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,gloomy season\Nthe forerunner of happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it joyful to\Nget married in June?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that the term June
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,originates from the goddess\NJuno in Roman mythology.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juno is known as Hera\Nin Greek mythology,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and oversees marriages\Nand childbirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, they say that those that\Nget married in the month of Hera,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,namely June, are protected\Nand blessed by the goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Hera is Zeus's wife, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.47,0:07:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an image of Hera\Nbeing a very jealous woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so to me, it doesn't feel really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a wedding, which would you like\Nto wear, a dress, or a kimono?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to wear a dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:08:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what I've been dreaming of\Never since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have to say a dress as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a kimono is nice too, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'd like to wear both.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that as of late,\Nthere are miniskirt versions,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and all sorts of colorful\Nwedding dresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Miniskirt wedding dresses...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it has a very frilly-edged design,\Nthat might be really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I have many dreams,\NI want a lot of frills," you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa is like Angel Salvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, from your hairdo\Nyou're more like Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the top should be yellow,\Nand the skirt should be a miniskirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa-{\i1}san {\i0}would look good\Nin a miniskirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The outfit is important,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what kind of person\Nyou marry is also important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A childhood friend,\Nor a girl from a rich family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to decide on which one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On one end, you have a huge dowry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can use magic like\NBeho_mi or I_nazun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, feeling-wise...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bianca, no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kagami, you're much\Nmore pure than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:09:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd run for\Nthe girl with the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have a comeback ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S'up, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a place I didn't get in\Nthat game I borrowed the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, wait a minute, Kagamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it fun because you solve\Nthings like that on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you understand\Nthe meaning of doing things yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you'll now do all your own\Nhomework, right, Konata?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detectives in manga and drama shows
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,keep running into murders,\Nfor some strange reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Conan and Kindaichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they didn't, the story\Nwouldn't go anywhere, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so? I think\Nnormal cases would work too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like running all over Japan\Nin search of a missing person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think following someone has\Na highly game-like aspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has thrill, and suspense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like accepting a request\Nfrom a husband to check out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whether or not his wife\Nis having an affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or looking for lost pets?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:10:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But would you enjoy watching\Nsomething like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, most likely it wouldn't be\Nany fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, and cases that happen in reality
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,usually don't use clever tricks\Nlike those in manga or TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like faking a fingerprint,\Nor fabricating something,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or eliminating luminol responses...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like spoofing even the\Nforensic investigation team.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, those that are really tough\Nget copycat criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so there's probably\Nsome media censorship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those perfect crimes end\Nwithout the public knowing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or remain unsolved, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a risky line, in all sorts of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you hate how there's\Nso much rain lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to like the rain\Nwhen I was little, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain gets you wet,\Nand your laundry can't get dry,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I never really liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}, why did\Nyou like it so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because rain would cancel\Nthe baseball broadcasts,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I could watch my anime\Nlike I normally do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's really like you\Nto say that, Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But nowadays, there are\Nso many domed stadiums...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Often in manga, you have\Nreally stupid characters
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and really smart characters\Nattending the same school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough outta you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Gourds at the top\Nof the vine should stay out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you think about it,\Nit's really strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you talk about that,\NI just saw this anime recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the teacher and\Nthe students are the same age,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how you thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, the teacher\Nactually looked younger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Miss Ta____ana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a well-known fact that\Nno matter who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people like to see the gap between\Nactual age and physical age.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, it's all the more\Nstrange to have students
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with different school scores\Nin the same class!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I really have\Nto agree on that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to say this, but I'm surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you actually got accepted\Nto this school, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at cramming,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so maybe you did the same\Nfor your entrance exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that really the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it took more than\None night of studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You surprised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm surprised that you\Nwere able to keep studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there an entrance exam prep\Ngame for the DS or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad gave me a couple of conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, a Pippin for a rank D school,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a 3DO for a rank C school,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a PS2 for a rank B school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi's dad really knows how\Nto control his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm even more surprised that\NTsukasa got into our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't it have been a little harder\Nfor you to say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--All right! I won again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Damn, I can't win if it's a fighting game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's put too much time into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can try me at anything,\Neven if it's not a fighting game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, next up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I challenge you to a quiz game!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost against Konata\Nin a game of wits?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it be... that she memorized\Nthe question patterns?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to games,\Nher memory's always top-notch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we play next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rummage through\Nstuff without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to have a really\Neasy party game, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.83,0:13:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you know which\Ngames someone has?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was something that even you\Nwould be able to win, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so smelly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, you haven't eaten\Nany sweets for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You usually eat so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no real reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it! You're dieting\Nto get ready for the summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even have someone\Nto show off your bathing suit to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You don't need to go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you two were born\Non the Star Festival day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost your birthday now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}, you remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seventeen years old, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seventeen is the year\Nbefore the unlucky year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens in the year\Nbefore your unlucky year?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the year where unlucky\Nthings start to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,right before your true unlucky year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As my birthday gets closer and\Ncloser, I get more uncertain,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I ended up buying all sorts\Nof goods to ward off evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and power stones, and stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kinda sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. As I kept buying,\Nit kinda became...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, we have that\NAlert Misfortune charm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait, it was the\NAvoid Misfortune charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alert Misfortune, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, "That's enough.\NSafe childbirth, safe driving,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's look all over all of it," and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that your birthdays\Nare on Ponytail Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why is it July 7?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that Orihime in the\NStar Festival legend had a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really farfetched...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There really is a Japan\NPonytail Association,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they give out the Japan\NPonytail Awards every year
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to a celebrity that looks\Ngood in a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think anyone would\Nlook good in a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the shortest hair,\Nso it's really cutting it close.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a small ponytail looks cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}, you look good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you'd be okay like that\Nin everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Fine.\NI should just take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look so manly, like a samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how drunks usually wrap\Ntheir neckties around their head?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any meaning behind that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that like when\Nthey loosen their ties,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it got stuck while they were\Ntrying to pull it off their heads?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to say that,\NI think people
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:16:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who always carry takeout boxes\Nare more unnatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeout boxes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those boxes that Kato-{\i1}chan\N{\i0}carries in the {\i1}Drifters {\i0}shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, the image of a drunk guy\Nis always with a tie around his head
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and carrying a takeout box.\NI don't know why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Orihime and Hikoboshi\Ncan see each other this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twinkle, twinkle...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I hope that Alert Misfortune\Ncharm will have good results.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a needless worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now the Comp-Fest is in the\Nmiddle of a QUO-card giveaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you\Nalways collect QUO-cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but do you ever use them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why do you bother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you blindly want goods from\Nyour favorites when they come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a fan, and as a collector.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, cards\Nthat you never use?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use it! You have\Nto safely stow it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I see people carelessly\Nusing them, it really pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Items like this should never be used!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And auctioning or selling them off\Nis out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, of course you fail as a fan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you also fail as a collector!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say it so passionately, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my case, I need\Nat least three cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One to keep for eternity,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I safely stow it away\Nin a special case just for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And one to pull out and\Nlook at every so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the third one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.56,0:17:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To spread the gospel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you really want something,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't you want to have two\Nor three of them, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, you don't.\NFine, I'm an otaku. I'm strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I vaguely understand\Nwhat you're trying to get at.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, you look like the type\Nthat would be popular with boys,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I never hear anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa is a bit plain, and\Nshe doesn't really stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because a scary-looking\Nsister is always guarding her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's not that I'm plain,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but more like Kona-{\i1}chan {\i0}and\NYuki-{\i1}chan {\i0}are very unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-{\i1}san {\i0}really knows\Na lot of stuff, and is pretty,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:18:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and has a nice figure, and really\Nwears glasses out of necessity,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--and hates dentists, and is clumsy,\Nand is a natural airhead...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:04.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey now, didn't that get a bit\Nstrange in the middle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, come to think of it, there\Naren't any rumors about Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe guys find it hard to approach\Nher because she's so pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so nice, and\Nlooks out for others so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.59,0:18:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's been asked out a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's saying no?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's saying no, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or when someone asks her out, she\Ndoesn't realize she's being asked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-{\i1}chan {\i0}tends to be a bit dense,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so guys have to tell her in\Na very straightforward way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, the boys in your class\Nare all so irresponsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't somebody in there\Nhave enough guts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to passionately state his feelings\Nand woo Miyuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we don't have that many\Nmaniac-types in our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl like Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0} is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a little more geared\Ntowards the maniac-types.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A maniac-type, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's already this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:18:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:19:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please don't mind me,\Nand continue to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laters!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, there was more\Nto that story, and he...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happens! I've done it before too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone does it at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done it too, right, Konata?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, that's\None part of her {\i1}moe{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.81,0:19:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Channel{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning Luckies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, today, we're starting\N{\i1}Lucky Channel {\i0}again
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with squeak-squeak-squeaky energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Akira Kogami,\Nyour navigator! And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm Minoru Shiraishi,\Nassistant to Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to see you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.12,0:20:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already the third time that\Nthe two of us have run the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Shiraishi-{\i1}san{\i0}?\NHave you gotten used to it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it seems like you really haven't
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,opened up your heart\Nto me yet, Shiraishi-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you're sitting a bit\Nfurther away from me than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this is the distance\Nbetween our hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the case, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'd like to start with\Na twinkle again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Today is a very\Nhappy project for all fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The introduction of the {\i1}Lucky Star\N{\i0}regular cast, first installment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Today, we are introducing\NMiss Miyuki Takara.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Class committee chair,\Nbeautiful appearance,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.66,0:20:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,gentle-spirited, obviously intelligent...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's "clearly intelligent."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clearly,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,good at literature and athletics,\Na perfect superhuman...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi-{\i1}san{\i0}, you know\Na lot about Miyuki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know a lot about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki is very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First off, those glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, when someone\Nis that beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you get the feeling that you\Nshouldn't be going near her,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she turns out to be\Nvery easygoing and friendly...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you would talk\Nthat much on the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Get you started on Miyuki,\Nand you can't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, it's nothing like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.77,0:21:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah... Was it\NMiss Miyuki Takara?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's one of those\Npretty-faced characters?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's got big breasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even her faults just\Nmake her more {\i1}moe{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm so jealous...\NThose beauty-type pretty women
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:25.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0}, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are also liked by the\Nmaniac-types too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when it comes to being\Nliked by the maniac-types,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,well, I have all the pedo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to say goodbye already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, in this segment, we always\Nseek questions and praise for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as your opinions of the show,\Nso please send them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then... Please look\Nforward to next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.67,0:21:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what is she actually like?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just like how I described her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding! She's not puffing out\Nwhite smoke from her nose
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the dressing room or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, on that point she's fine,\Nshe's not like you, Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.70,0:21:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.16,0:22:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a unique song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.87,0:22:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to hear a song that is\Neasy on ordinary people's ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.94,0:22:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll know the next song, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's guess what it is from the intro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope this isn't another strange song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.20,0:22:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.08,0:22:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.29,0:22:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, Kagamin, what's the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's {\i1}Full Metal{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Full Metal{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.41,0:22:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, it's Kagami's\Nfavorite, {\i1}Fumoffu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.73,0:22:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.98,0:22:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just read the novel a bit,\Nand was only slightly hooked!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.67,0:22:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ For instance, on days \Nwhere tears drop ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.38,0:22:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}, you're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can get a very mature voice out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.72,0:22:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's just impersonating the singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.18,0:22:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I want to have that \Nback all to myself ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.44,0:22:49.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Tsukasa, Miyuki, what \Nare you going to sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.77,0:22:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can sing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.63,0:22:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know that many songs, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what kind of song it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.28,0:22:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata's like that, so we \Nshould sing what we like too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.20,0:23:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll try looking for something!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.48,0:23:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not very confident in my singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.79,0:23:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.15,0:23:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be the only ones \Nlistening, so relax and sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.08,0:23:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ If you can see a rainbow\Nin town after the rain ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.30,0:23:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Let's start walking now ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.25,0:23:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Something's about to begin ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.46,0:23:31.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Episode Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what's with\Nthe next episode of {\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.53,0:23:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the other day, there was\Nsomething that I laughed at so hard
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I thought I would stop breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.00,0:23:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At school, in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any time left?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode:\NA Question of Motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:43.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Question of Motivation"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to it!
